        "TileImage": "$($repository 645d1646-c910-4d8a-9f9a-b39aca226eef).Image",
        "Description": "After your last encounter, Reed has fled south to Argentina and has been spotted in a Vineyard in Mendoza. And to add to the situation, Reed has been escorted by 4 elite bodygaurds, who will do anything to protect him. Reed is going by the alias Augusto Albarez and is staying around his 2 bodygaurds. All of them are in perfect sight of Reed&apos;s snipers so attempting to eleminate him without taking out them out would be foolish. Good luck.",
